---
title: Beef & Mushroom Red Pesto Penne with Parmesan
description: Put your best-o foot forward with this gorgeous pesto. We’ve livened up a classic pasta dish with red pesto, tender mushrooms and a sprinkling of Parmesan. You’re going to impress even your toughest critic with this flavoursome offering

*Unfortunately, this week's spaghetti and courgette were in short supply, so we've replaced them with penne and baby spinach. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
